| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181202112822/http://corporate.britannica.com/britannica_nature_response.pdf
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>，但部份現今的版本內容的準確性仍然受到質疑<ref name="kister_1994" /><ref name="Giles_Nature_study_2005">{{cite journal
| url = http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v438/n7070/full/438900a.html
